Armor Expert	KEY:Armor Expert ~ Trait	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Armor Expert ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]	DESC:You have worn armor as long as you can remember, either as part of your training to become a knight's squire or simply because you were seeking to emulate a hero.																											BONUS:MISC|ACCHECK|1	SOURCEPAGE:p.327	BENEFIT:You have worn armor as long as you can remember, either as part of your training to become a knight's squire or simply because you were seeking to emulate a hero. When you wear armor of any sort, reduce that suit's armor check penalty by 1, to a minimum check penalty of 0.
Bullied		KEY:Bullied ~ Trait		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Bullied ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]		DESC:You were bullied often as a child, and you are now constantly ready to defend yourself with your fists when an enemy comes near.																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.328	BENEFIT:You were bullied often as a child, and you are now constantly ready to defend yourself with your fists when an enemy comes near. You gain a +1 trait bonus on attacks of opportunity attack rolls made with unarmed strikes. Note that this trait does not grant the ability to make attacks of opportunity with your unarmed strikes.
Courageous		KEY:Courageous ~ Trait		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Courageous ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]	DESC:Your childhood was brutal, yet you persevered primarily through force of will and the hope that no matter how hard things might get, as long as you kept a level head you'd make it through.																										SOURCEPAGE:p.328	BENEFIT:Your childhood was brutal, yet you persevered primarily through force of will and the hope that no matter how hard things might get, as long as you kept a level head you'd make it through. You gain a +2 trait bonus on saving throws against fear effects.
Deft Dodger		KEY:Deft Dodger ~ Trait		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Deft Dodger ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]	DESC:Growing up in a rough neighborhood or a dangerous environment has honed your senses.																											BONUS:CHECKS|Reflex|1|TYPE=Trait												SOURCEPAGE:p.328	BENEFIT:Growing up in a rough neighborhood or a dangerous environment has honed your senses. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Reflex saves.
Dirty Fighter	KEY:Dirty Fighter ~ Trait	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Dirty Fighter ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]	DESC:You wouldn't have lived to make it out of childhood without the aid of a sibling, friend, or companion on whom you could always count to distract your enemies long enough to do a little bit more damage than normal.																						SOURCEPAGE:p.328	BENEFIT:You wouldn't have lived to make it out of childhood without the aid of a sibling, friend, or companion on whom you could always count to distract your enemies long enough to do a little bit more damage than normal. When you hit a foe you are flanking, you deal an additional 1 point of damage (this damage is added to your base damage, and is multiplied on a critical hit). This additional damage is a trait bonus.
Fencer		KEY:Fencer ~ Trait		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Fencer ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]		DESC:You trained long hours as a youth with blades, either taking lessons in the genteel art of fencing from tutors paid for by your parents or by being taken under the wing of a disenfranchised fencer who may have turned to a life of crime.																		SOURCEPAGE:p.328	BENEFIT:You trained long hours as a youth with blades, either taking lessons in the genteel art of fencing from tutors paid for by your parents or by being taken under the wing of a disenfranchised fencer who may have turned to a life of crime. You gain a +1 trait bonus on attacks of opportunity made with daggers, swords, and similar bladed weapons.
Killer		KEY:Killer ~ Trait		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Killer ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]		DESC:You made your first kill at a very young age and found the task of war or murder to your liking.																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.328	BENEFIT:You made your first kill at a very young age and found the task of war or murder to your liking. You deal additional damage equal to your weapon's critical hit modifier when you score a successful critical hit with a weapon; this additional damage is added to the final total, and is not multiplied by the critical hit multiple itself. This extra damage is a trait bonus.
Reactionary		KEY:Reactionary ~ Trait		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Reactionary ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]	DESC:You were bullied often as a child, but never quite developed an offensive response. Instead, you became adept at anticipating sudden attacks and reacting to danger quickly.																		BONUS:COMBAT|INITIATIVE|2|TYPE=Trait					SOURCEPAGE:p.328	BENEFIT:You were bullied often as a child, but never quite developed an offensive response. Instead, you became adept at anticipating sudden attacks and reacting to danger quickly. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Initiative checks.
Resilient		KEY:Resilient ~ Trait		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Resilient ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait]		DESC:Growing up in a violent neighborhood or in the unforgiving wilds often forced you to subsist on food and water from doubtful sources.																		BONUS:CHECKS|Fortitude|1|TYPE=Trait												SOURCEPAGE:p.328	BENEFIT:Growing up in a violent neighborhood or in the unforgiving wilds often forced you to subsist on food and water from doubtful sources. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Fortitude saves.

