Birthmark				KEY:Birthmark ~ Trait				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Birthmark ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]				DESC:You were born with a strange birthmark that looks very similar to the holy symbol of the god you chose to worship later in life.																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.328	BENEFIT:You were born with a strange birthmark that looks very similar to the holy symbol of the god you chose to worship later in life. You gain a +2 trait bonus on all saving throws against charm and compulsion effects as a result.
