Ear for Music (Shelyn)					KEY:Ear for Music ~ Trait			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.ReligionTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Ear for Music ~ Trait],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.ReligionTrait]			DESC:You spent countless hours of your youth in one of Shelyn's temples, listening to wonderful musicians and singers. You gain a +1 trait bonus on one category of Perform checks and a +2 trait bonus on any Knowledge (local) checks that deal with the local art or music scene.																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.333
